Invocation Name: west virginia secretary of states office
des: With this skill, you can ask many different questions about the West Virginia Secretary of State’s Office. The first step is to enable the skill. To enable the skill, say, ‘Alexa, enable West Virginia Secretary of State’s Office.’ To access the skill after the skill is enabled, say, ‘Alexa, launch West Virginia Secretary of State’s Office.’ After launching the skill, you can begin asking various questions about the office like how to register to vote, how to register a business, what are the various filing fees, or even contact information for a specific West Virginia county clerk or Chamber of Commerce.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
